### Test Elderly Assistant API
### You can use VS Code REST Client extension or any HTTP client like Postman

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:5000

###

### Get all reminders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reminders

###

### Create a new reminder
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicineName": "Aspirin",
  "time": "08:00",
  "note": "Take with food"
}

###

### Create another reminder
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicineName": "Blood Pressure Medicine",
  "time": "20:00",
  "note": "Take before dinner"
}

###

### Get a single reminder (replace :id with actual reminder ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/YOUR_REMINDER_ID_HERE

###

### Update a reminder (replace :id with actual reminder ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/YOUR_REMINDER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicineName": "Aspirin Updated",
  "time": "09:00",
  "note": "Take with breakfast"
}

###

### Delete a reminder (replace :id with actual reminder ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/reminders/YOUR_REMINDER_ID_HERE

###

